posting_body: ['Newly Updated Seattle 2 Bed Unit!', 'Property Address', '9020 20th Ave SW Unit 102 | Seattle, WA 98106-2327', 'Available: Now', 'Offered By', 'Lakeshore Corporation', 'Description', "Don't miss out on this opportunity to lease an ideally located 2 bed Seattle unit!", 'Featuring updated countertops, and flooring, this unit also has a deck with territorial views!', "Located in White Center near Highland Park, you'll enjoy everything that the area has to offer including plenty of parks, retail, restaurants, entertainment, and more!", 'Monthly Rent: $1,825 + $75 flat monthly fee for W/S/G and $25 flat monthly fee for storage.', 'Deposit: $1250 ( $250 non-refundable fee)', 'Lease Term: 12 Months', 'Pets accepted on a case-by-case basis with additional fee(s) and/or pet rent (1 pet maximum; 30 lb. limit.)', 'Tenants pays electric.', '$49 non-refundable application fee per each applicant age 18 and older.', 'Key Words: Seattle, White Center, South Delridge, Roxhill, Highland Park, Lakeshore.', 'Amenities', 'Updated Countertops', 'New Flooring', 'Deck with Territorial View', 'Coin-operated Laundry On-site', 'Secured Entry', '1 Assigned Parking Space', 'Details', 'Beds/Baths: 2BD/1.0BA', 'Square Feet: 865', 'Rental Terms', 'Rent: $1,825.00', 'Available: Now', 'Application Fee: $49.00', 'Security Deposit: $1,000.00', 'Pet Policy', 'Cats allowed', 'Small dogs allowed']
